data.description: Welcome home! Come see this stunning turn-key 4/3 pool home in the desirable neighborhood of North Palmetto Bay. This home’s features include the family rooms high vaulted ceiling with exposed beams adds a touch of elegance and character to the living space. The inclusion of a chef's kitchen with hi-end appliances and custom wood cabinetry. You’ll find ample sized bedrooms. Recently updated master bathroom and walk-in closet. The backyard opens from a screened-in patio with a saltwater pool and beautiful landscaping is the epitome of outdoor living. The conversion to a green home is a fantastic feature. Having 2 central A/C units, solar panels, and 2 Tesla solar batteries, impact windows and doors not only reduces the environmental impact but also has an amazing FPL monthly bill of $29.00.
